WEBVTT

01:43.039 --> 01:46.009
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.140 --> 01:49.009
[Episode 29]

01:49.240 --> 01:50.039
[Peng]

01:50.039 --> 01:52.000
[Peng, I saw a boy on the street today. He looks like you when you were young]

01:52.000 --> 01:54.500
[Peng, you'll have time off for Christmas, right? Are you coming back to China?]

01:52.000 --> 01:54.500
[If you do, make sure to contact Mom, okay?]

01:54.530 --> 01:57.160
[Call me when you're free, okay?]

01:54.530 --> 01:57.160
[Peng, I wanted to call you today, but I was afraid to disturb you]

02:16.630 --> 02:17.750
All right.

02:17.810 --> 02:18.610
Stop crying.

02:19.900 --> 02:21.140
It's bad for your health.

02:24.800 --> 02:26.440
It's my fault.

02:27.970 --> 02:29.250
But you know

02:30.030 --> 02:30.840
we had no choice

02:32.110 --> 02:33.670
at that time, right?

02:33.710 --> 02:34.470
I know. I know.

02:34.510 --> 02:35.460
I know it all.

02:36.700 --> 02:37.470
You have always felt guilty

02:37.490 --> 02:38.930
toward Peng.

02:40.110 --> 02:41.470
But it's all in the past.

02:41.490 --> 02:43.000
We can't change anything.

02:44.190 --> 02:45.200
Look forward.

02:45.370 --> 02:46.960
Look forward.

02:47.350 --> 02:48.630
As long as we

02:48.810 --> 02:50.610
treat him sincerely,

02:50.640 --> 02:52.440
he will accept you in the end.

02:56.750 --> 02:57.690
Do you think

02:59.750 --> 03:01.390
he hates me?

03:02.680 --> 03:03.960
Otherwise, why hasn't he replied to

03:03.990 --> 03:05.750
any of my messages for such a long time?

03:05.830 --> 03:06.790
No matter how much he hates you,

03:06.810 --> 03:08.560
he's still your son.

03:08.580 --> 03:09.250
How about this?

03:09.800 --> 03:10.710
When you get better,

03:11.270 --> 03:12.080
I'll accompany you

03:12.190 --> 03:13.520
to go find him.

03:13.620 --> 03:14.700
No matter what issues you have between you,

03:14.750 --> 03:16.460
just talk it out.

03:16.920 --> 03:17.450
Okay?

03:18.960 --> 03:19.760
Okay, wipe your tears.

03:19.800 --> 03:20.640
Wipe them clean.

03:22.250 --> 03:25.329
I really feel bad.

03:25.390 --> 03:26.750
Look at him.

03:27.750 --> 03:28.350
Alright.

03:28.370 --> 03:29.650
Enough.

03:29.760 --> 03:30.810
Alright.

03:31.510 --> 03:33.320
I'll go with you for everything.

03:33.350 --> 03:34.110
Okay?

03:35.270 --> 03:36.120
I'm here.

03:37.570 --> 03:39.250
All right.

04:12.830 --> 04:13.350
Sorry.

04:13.350 --> 04:14.430
You can't go in here.

04:15.910 --> 04:16.690
Who is this?

04:16.950 --> 04:17.660
Who knows?

04:20.390 --> 04:20.860
Let's go.

04:23.230 --> 04:23.710
What's wrong?

04:24.720 --> 04:25.440
I don't know.

04:28.200 --> 04:29.110
What are you looking at?

04:29.710 --> 04:30.420
Mr. Wen,

04:31.070 --> 04:32.610
that woman has been here since early this morning.

04:32.640 --> 04:34.350
She's been standing downstairs all the time.

04:46.530 --> 04:47.100
Drive her away.

04:48.409 --> 04:50.060
Drive her away!

04:52.390 --> 04:53.050
Yes.

04:58.210 --> 05:00.080
I know. I won't barge in.

05:00.140 --> 05:00.790
But…

05:00.870 --> 05:02.270
I really need to talk to Mr. Wen.

05:02.290 --> 05:02.840
Can you

05:02.870 --> 05:04.230
find a colleague in charge to…

05:04.910 --> 05:06.710
May I help you?

05:09.190 --> 05:10.230
I’m looking for Mr. Wen.

05:12.390 --> 05:13.070
Sorry.

05:13.230 --> 05:14.220
We don't

05:14.320 --> 05:15.250
have this person here.

05:17.590 --> 05:18.990
I searched online.

05:20.990 --> 05:22.370
Your boss's surname is Wen.

05:23.110 --> 05:24.270
He's named Wen Peng.

05:25.390 --> 05:26.030
Just help me…

05:26.030 --> 05:26.630
I don't know

05:26.630 --> 05:28.020
where you found that information.

05:28.470 --> 05:29.660
However,

05:29.830 --> 05:31.680
there really is no such person here.

05:31.980 --> 05:33.080
You're standing here,

05:33.110 --> 05:34.670
blocking our company's vehicles

05:34.710 --> 05:35.590
and people from getting in and out.

05:35.780 --> 05:36.580
So,

05:37.270 --> 05:38.590
please leave.

06:06.710 --> 06:12.380
[Peng, I know you're in Ninghai. Can you meet me?]

06:19.830 --> 06:20.740
Peng.

06:21.280 --> 06:23.030
I know you're in Ninghai.

06:23.050 --> 06:25.830
Can you meet me?

07:30.510 --> 07:31.380
Look.

07:31.800 --> 07:33.130
You look so sad.

07:35.510 --> 07:36.450
Don't be sad.

07:36.950 --> 07:37.760
So…

07:39.590 --> 07:41.130
he has been in Ninghai the whole time.

07:41.830 --> 07:43.190
He knows I'm looking for him.

07:46.920 --> 07:48.470
He just doesn't want to see me.

07:51.909 --> 07:53.330
If I knew this would happen,

07:56.470 --> 07:57.520
I shouldn't have

07:57.560 --> 07:58.790
left him alone back then.

08:00.870 --> 08:01.580
No matter how hard it was,

08:03.060 --> 08:04.820
I should've taken him with me.

08:06.510 --> 08:07.140
Mom,

08:09.400 --> 08:10.240
I don't think

08:10.270 --> 08:11.470
it's all your fault.

08:12.710 --> 08:14.060
Don't blame yourself.

08:14.930 --> 08:16.620
It's not like you didn't go back to look for him.

08:16.680 --> 08:17.630
You did.

08:17.790 --> 08:18.720
You just didn't find him.

08:19.430 --> 08:20.330
His father

08:20.510 --> 08:21.390
took him away.

08:21.410 --> 08:22.860
He just didn't want him to see you.

08:23.480 --> 08:25.050
What could you have done?

08:33.110 --> 08:33.870
It's okay.

08:34.510 --> 08:35.559
Now,

08:36.250 --> 08:37.159
we meet him again.

08:37.530 --> 08:38.480
Now, we know

08:38.510 --> 08:39.470
he's in Ninghai.

08:40.049 --> 08:40.970
We met again.

08:41.990 --> 08:45.140
You'll have plenty of time to make up for him.

08:45.910 --> 08:46.430
Right?

08:54.560 --> 08:55.390
Yes.

09:03.540 --> 09:04.260
Professor Yu,

09:04.620 --> 09:06.030
we'll be in Chengzhou soon.

09:06.390 --> 09:07.190
Where should we go first?

09:08.050 --> 09:09.680
Let's go to the sports school first.

09:10.270 --> 09:10.780
Okay.

09:11.800 --> 09:12.650
Are you hungry?

09:12.720 --> 09:13.990
Do you want to eat first?

09:14.190 --> 09:15.030
I'm not hungry.

09:15.670 --> 09:16.560
Let's go there first.

09:17.470 --> 09:17.920
Okay.

09:20.760 --> 09:21.390
This is

09:21.420 --> 09:22.240
Li Ruonan you're looking for.

09:25.760 --> 09:27.240
She is my most talented student

09:27.510 --> 09:28.750
in all these years.

09:30.220 --> 09:31.450
She's really good,

09:31.480 --> 09:32.390
but she's not moral.

09:32.430 --> 09:33.290
She almost stabbed me to death.

09:33.310 --> 09:34.320
Of course she's good.

09:34.800 --> 09:36.330
She was gifted.

09:36.410 --> 09:36.950
Later,

09:36.990 --> 09:38.350
she practiced harder than anyone else.

09:39.010 --> 09:39.680
Unfortunately,

09:39.710 --> 09:40.750
such a promising young athlete…

09:40.770 --> 09:41.790
What a pity.

09:42.150 --> 09:42.890
What happened to her?

09:43.110 --> 09:44.130
It's about her family.

09:44.510 --> 09:45.140
Her father

09:45.200 --> 09:45.710
passed away early.

09:46.290 --> 09:46.830
My mother

09:46.870 --> 09:48.090
is always sick.

09:48.630 --> 09:49.560
In the end, she had no choice

09:49.740 --> 09:51.070
but to drop out.

09:51.590 --> 09:52.550
Do you know

09:52.570 --> 09:54.210
what disease her mother got?

09:54.830 --> 09:55.880
As for the details,

09:55.960 --> 09:57.010
I'm not sure.

09:59.820 --> 10:00.490
Let me show you this.

10:00.520 --> 10:02.180
This is the photo of her and her mother.

10:08.070 --> 10:08.750
Coach,

10:08.950 --> 10:11.020
can we have this?

10:11.050 --> 10:11.580
Sure.

10:11.610 --> 10:12.200
Thank you.

10:12.600 --> 10:13.050
Okay.

10:13.630 --> 10:14.170
Thank you.

10:14.200 --> 10:14.990
-Thank you, Coach.
-You're welcome.

10:15.030 --> 10:15.630
Okay.

10:16.390 --> 10:17.370
Bye.

10:17.510 --> 10:17.870
Okay.

10:18.730 --> 10:21.000
So, she dropped out

10:21.350 --> 10:22.290
because her mother was sick?

10:22.590 --> 10:23.350
That's right.

10:23.640 --> 10:24.650
She would rather drop out of school

10:24.680 --> 10:25.790
to take care of her mother.

10:26.350 --> 10:27.390
It seems that she was close

10:27.250 --> 10:29.550
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

10:27.390 --> 10:28.310
to her mother.

10:28.870 --> 10:29.680
I guess…

10:29.990 --> 10:31.920
after Wen Peng saw her

10:31.950 --> 10:33.310
hit the assistant director,

10:33.330 --> 10:34.700
he thought she was good at martial arts,

10:34.960 --> 10:36.440
so he helped her to settle the problem with money

10:36.470 --> 10:37.420
in order to buy her over.

10:38.410 --> 10:39.670
If she dropped out

10:39.710 --> 10:41.330
because of her mother's illness,

10:41.690 --> 10:42.480
then...

10:43.110 --> 10:44.040
now that she committed a crime

10:44.070 --> 10:44.990
and needed to go to jail,

10:45.590 --> 10:46.220
she definitely considered

10:46.260 --> 10:47.440
who would take care of her mother.

10:47.730 --> 10:48.880
Have you checked this line?

10:49.240 --> 10:50.010
Yes.

10:50.630 --> 10:51.190
That's why I decided

10:51.190 --> 10:52.270
to start from this direction.

10:53.600 --> 10:54.660
How's it going on your side?

10:56.360 --> 10:57.430
I...

10:58.110 --> 10:58.940
Not bad.

11:00.030 --> 11:01.160
Since I knew

11:01.200 --> 11:02.590
that Wen Peng is

11:02.860 --> 11:04.250
my mother's biological son,

11:05.270 --> 11:06.590
I've thought it through.

11:07.240 --> 11:08.240
What have you thought through?

11:08.810 --> 11:10.080
His criminal motive.

11:10.880 --> 11:12.490
If he is the murderer,

11:12.520 --> 11:14.520
his motive is me.

11:15.980 --> 11:17.180
This should be all.

11:17.230 --> 11:19.340
You can check

11:19.480 --> 11:20.830
and ask him what other questions he has.

11:23.540 --> 11:24.330
Auntie.

11:25.850 --> 11:27.960
Lu, I was looking for you.

11:30.270 --> 11:31.080
Lu.

11:31.700 --> 11:32.920
I need…

11:34.000 --> 11:35.570
a favor from you.

11:36.260 --> 11:37.030
No problem.

11:37.230 --> 11:37.750
Go ahead.

11:37.830 --> 11:38.480
What is it?

11:40.030 --> 11:40.430
I...

11:41.870 --> 11:42.630
I think...

11:45.190 --> 11:47.080
Can you help me find Peng?

11:48.550 --> 11:49.070
Auntie…

11:49.110 --> 11:49.960
I know

11:50.050 --> 11:51.670
this is putting you in a difficult place.

11:52.890 --> 11:54.720
I went to his company to find him.

11:54.740 --> 11:56.530
They stopped me from seeing him.

11:56.610 --> 11:57.290
I...

11:57.760 --> 11:58.300
I...

11:58.350 --> 11:59.870
I have no other way.

11:59.890 --> 12:00.850
I know

12:00.880 --> 12:02.490
you and Peng are alumni.

12:02.510 --> 12:04.190
Can you give him a call for me?

12:04.230 --> 12:04.670
Auntie…

12:04.690 --> 12:05.230
Ask him out

12:05.230 --> 12:07.000
so that I can meet him, okay?

12:07.030 --> 12:07.640
Auntie,

12:07.970 --> 12:08.470
I...

12:08.470 --> 12:09.630
I'm begging you.

12:10.260 --> 12:11.410
Please help me.

12:11.470 --> 12:12.180
Okay?

12:12.580 --> 12:13.820
Please help me.

12:14.590 --> 12:15.070
Okay?

12:15.150 --> 12:15.780
No. No.

12:15.800 --> 12:17.050
Auntie, don't be like this.

12:17.910 --> 12:19.600
I'll call him…

12:19.650 --> 12:20.570
for you.

12:21.550 --> 12:22.260
Okay.

12:22.820 --> 12:23.500
Okay.

12:24.730 --> 12:25.700
Mr. Wen.

12:27.620 --> 12:29.670
Er, do you have time tonight?

12:30.660 --> 12:31.450
Yes.

12:33.150 --> 12:34.720
Can we have dinner together?

12:35.630 --> 12:36.260
Sure.

12:36.550 --> 12:37.450
What do you want to eat?

12:37.480 --> 12:38.160
My treat.

12:38.830 --> 12:39.510
Okay.

12:39.610 --> 12:40.510
I'll send you

12:40.530 --> 12:41.520
the address later.

12:41.790 --> 12:42.480
Okay.

12:51.550 --> 12:52.830
Auntie, I'm done.

12:53.530 --> 12:54.990
I'll send you the address later.

12:55.840 --> 12:56.560
Okay.

12:57.030 --> 12:57.940
Lu,

12:58.490 --> 13:00.140
don't tell him you're with me.

13:00.170 --> 13:00.790
Otherwise...

13:00.820 --> 13:02.100
I didn't say anything.

13:02.370 --> 13:03.820
I just invited him to dinner.

13:06.370 --> 13:07.270
Well...

13:07.760 --> 13:08.670
Lu,

13:09.180 --> 13:09.850
can you…

13:10.710 --> 13:12.560
go with me tonight?

13:12.590 --> 13:14.880
I'm afraid that Peng...

13:22.670 --> 13:24.070
[Anshan Branch, Ninghai Public Security]

13:24.730 --> 13:26.890
[Notice of the Ninghai Public Security Bureau's Decision to Lift the Residential Surveillance]

13:33.960 --> 13:36.860
[Lu Yan]

13:38.090 --> 13:39.630
Auntie came to me today

13:39.650 --> 13:41.490
and begged me because she wanted to see Wen Peng.

13:41.950 --> 13:43.020
I had no choice

13:43.070 --> 13:44.140
but to agree.

13:57.020 --> 13:59.300
[Italian Restaurant]

14:03.590 --> 14:04.230
Lu Yan.

14:04.670 --> 14:05.750
-Mr. Wen.
-You're finally willing to see me.

14:07.540 --> 14:08.410
Actually,

14:08.870 --> 14:11.390
it's not me who wants to see you today.

14:12.550 --> 14:13.190
Then, who is it?

14:23.160 --> 14:24.200
Peng.

14:34.880 --> 14:36.070
Chengyi, you're here, too?

14:42.300 --> 14:43.300
Mr. Wen,

14:46.390 --> 14:48.220
have a good chat with Auntie.

14:48.460 --> 14:49.860
Give her another chance.

15:07.510 --> 15:08.230
You must be hungry.

15:11.290 --> 15:12.670
Eat something.

15:22.830 --> 15:23.710
All these years,

15:26.740 --> 15:28.560
I've imagined countless times

15:29.810 --> 15:31.530
what it'd be like to see My Peng again,

15:34.280 --> 15:36.360
but no matter how much I imagined,

15:36.840 --> 15:37.910
it never came close to the amazing person

15:37.990 --> 15:38.960
you are right now.

15:45.060 --> 15:46.210
I heard

15:46.280 --> 15:48.090
when you were in college,

15:48.250 --> 15:50.250
your major grades were always among the top few each year,

15:50.310 --> 15:51.910
and you got a scholarship every year.

15:52.150 --> 15:52.940
Moreover,

15:53.070 --> 15:55.200
you made it to the school team for basketball.

15:55.880 --> 15:57.350
You were even a student council officer.

15:57.790 --> 15:58.390
Am I right?

16:01.970 --> 16:03.480
At that time,

16:03.510 --> 16:04.990
you studied medicine.

16:05.390 --> 16:07.200
Why didn't you become a doctor after you graduated?

16:08.790 --> 16:09.710
Does it have anything to do with you?

16:18.310 --> 16:18.860
You're right.

16:22.480 --> 16:23.940
As your mother,

16:26.830 --> 16:28.230
I'm not qualified at all.

16:33.430 --> 16:34.790
They told me

16:37.070 --> 16:38.470
you went abroad to study.

16:39.560 --> 16:40.870
I can only get some of your news

16:40.910 --> 16:42.110
from your aunt.

16:42.550 --> 16:44.600
I asked her for your WeChat account.

16:45.270 --> 16:46.070
Every time...

16:46.560 --> 16:47.950
Every time I sent you a message,

16:47.990 --> 16:48.470
you didn't reply.

16:48.510 --> 16:50.070
I thought it was due to the time difference.

16:50.110 --> 16:50.800
Peng,

16:51.060 --> 16:52.550
don't blame me.

16:52.550 --> 16:54.420
It's not that I didn't care about you.

16:54.750 --> 16:55.470
Actually,

16:55.880 --> 16:56.910
when I just left,

16:56.930 --> 16:58.450
I went back to look for you.

16:58.470 --> 17:00.310
I even called the police to find you.

17:00.350 --> 17:01.160
You know?

17:01.190 --> 17:01.910
But…

17:02.500 --> 17:03.590
your dad said

17:04.390 --> 17:05.250
if

17:05.609 --> 17:07.369
I dare to look for you again,

17:09.780 --> 17:10.460
he will...

17:11.290 --> 17:12.440
beat you to death

17:13.900 --> 17:15.349
in front of me.

17:17.690 --> 17:19.010
I was scared...

17:19.369 --> 17:20.930
I was scared that he'd hurt you.

17:20.990 --> 17:21.829
You know

17:21.849 --> 17:23.190
he's capable of anything.

17:23.220 --> 17:24.109
You know what he was like

17:24.150 --> 17:25.030
when you were young.

17:25.069 --> 17:25.829
-Right, Peng?
-Yes.

17:25.859 --> 17:26.980
-Please forgive me.
-I know. I know.

17:27.010 --> 17:28.040
I'm not…

17:28.820 --> 17:29.350
Yes.

17:32.420 --> 17:33.510
You have your reasons.

17:33.550 --> 17:34.470
You all have your reasons.

17:36.460 --> 17:37.100
What about me?

17:42.410 --> 17:43.150
Actually,

17:43.150 --> 17:44.270
I saw you when you came

17:44.400 --> 17:45.260
to my company today.

17:46.800 --> 17:47.640
But I asked my assistant

17:47.670 --> 17:48.580
to drive you away.

17:48.950 --> 17:49.790
Do you know why?

17:53.950 --> 17:55.250
Because you came too late.

17:58.140 --> 17:59.640
If it were 20 years ago,

17:59.670 --> 18:01.070
I would go to you without hesitation.

18:01.110 --> 18:01.800
But…

18:02.480 --> 18:03.150
now we have

18:03.190 --> 18:04.310
no connection anymore.

18:06.150 --> 18:07.580
But we do!

18:08.840 --> 18:09.980
Mom found Peng.

18:11.030 --> 18:12.510
Give me a chance.

18:12.530 --> 18:13.240
Okay?

18:14.600 --> 18:15.750
Let me take care of you.

18:15.770 --> 18:16.980
Give me a chance.

18:17.050 --> 18:17.710
Alright.

18:18.920 --> 18:20.380
Since we've met,

18:20.400 --> 18:21.460
let's make things clear.

18:23.010 --> 18:23.700
Okay.

18:25.330 --> 18:27.050
Do you know what my life was like

18:27.960 --> 18:28.960
after you left?

18:30.840 --> 18:32.430
How did I live?

18:34.950 --> 18:36.820
I didn't dare to sleep every night.

18:38.310 --> 18:40.180
I could only go back to bed secretly.

18:41.170 --> 18:42.470
But I couldn't wake him up.

18:43.240 --> 18:44.600
If I woke him up,

18:44.750 --> 18:45.790
I would get a harsh beating

18:47.050 --> 18:48.110
He hit me

18:48.230 --> 18:49.270
with whatever was beside the bed.

18:50.330 --> 18:51.690
Sometimes it was a belt;

18:51.790 --> 18:53.270
sometimes, a rattan stick;

18:53.470 --> 18:54.700
sometimes,

18:55.750 --> 18:56.610
a wine bottle.

19:08.570 --> 19:09.790
Do you know what he said to me

19:09.810 --> 19:10.860
when he hit me?

19:13.300 --> 19:14.160
He said I was something

19:14.190 --> 19:15.460
that no one wanted.

19:18.250 --> 19:19.720
He also said

19:19.750 --> 19:21.210
I betrayed him

19:22.900 --> 19:24.000
by letting you go.

19:25.810 --> 19:26.250
I...

19:27.010 --> 19:27.740
Mom…

19:28.200 --> 19:29.060
I want...

19:29.350 --> 19:30.390
I want you.

19:35.810 --> 19:36.910
Actually, when I was 17,

19:36.950 --> 19:37.640
I saw you.

19:39.300 --> 19:40.820
When I went to your house that day,

19:42.520 --> 19:44.130
I saw you and Jiang Chengyi.

19:54.030 --> 19:55.030
What's wrong?

19:55.050 --> 19:56.910
You look upset. Are you unhappy?

20:01.270 --> 20:01.940
Perfect.

20:01.980 --> 20:03.540
I can ask Granny to persuade my dad.

20:06.750 --> 20:08.630
Do you want to go to the police academy that badly?

20:09.960 --> 20:11.470
I've always wanted to since I was little.

20:11.740 --> 20:13.240
My dad agreed to it before.

20:13.270 --> 20:14.560
Why did he suddenly change his mind?

20:17.190 --> 20:17.910
Fine.

20:18.510 --> 20:19.550
I promise you

20:19.640 --> 20:20.870
I'll tell your grandma.

20:21.560 --> 20:22.540
However,

20:22.750 --> 20:23.920
you have to promise me

20:24.170 --> 20:25.560
if your grandma agrees,

20:25.900 --> 20:27.760
you'll eat two more

20:27.790 --> 20:28.920
drumsticks your grandma made.

20:29.200 --> 20:29.930
Okay?

20:31.390 --> 20:32.310
Deal.

20:32.830 --> 20:33.960
You silly boy.

20:34.580 --> 20:35.700
Okay, let's go.

20:49.640 --> 20:51.270
At that time, I thought,

20:53.210 --> 20:54.440
now that you had a new family—

20:56.770 --> 20:58.220
a new son

20:58.800 --> 20:59.860
and a new husband,

21:01.290 --> 21:02.610
you didn't need me anymore.

21:03.950 --> 21:05.730
So, you just said

21:05.800 --> 21:07.200
you'd been looking for me all these years.

21:07.230 --> 21:08.650
Do you think I'll believe you?

21:08.770 --> 21:10.440
Do you think I'd reply

21:10.520 --> 21:11.910
to those messages you sent me?

21:12.430 --> 21:13.470
You brought those two here

21:13.510 --> 21:14.500
to see me.

21:14.530 --> 21:15.880
What do you want to tell me by doing that?

21:16.270 --> 21:17.110
Do you want to show me

21:17.150 --> 21:18.260
how happy you are now?

21:18.260 --> 21:18.830
Do you?

21:18.920 --> 21:19.630
No.

21:28.630 --> 21:29.390
Fine, I don't want to hear it.

21:29.430 --> 21:30.430
I don't want to hear your explanation.

21:33.870 --> 21:34.600
Look at me.

21:35.830 --> 21:37.060
I'm doing well.

21:37.970 --> 21:38.750
The gold watch.

21:39.630 --> 21:41.340
Everyone revolves around me.

21:41.470 --> 21:43.030
They cater to my every need

21:43.060 --> 21:44.150
and take care of everything for me every day.

21:45.470 --> 21:46.510
I don't need you.

21:49.550 --> 21:51.130
So, this is the last time

21:51.390 --> 21:52.360
I see you.

21:53.330 --> 21:54.650
This is the last time we meet.

21:57.100 --> 21:58.260
Thank you

21:58.720 --> 22:00.580
for bringing me

22:01.160 --> 22:03.960
all the sadness and fear.

22:04.740 --> 22:05.730
Everything.

22:09.830 --> 22:10.630
Here's to you.

22:20.670 --> 22:21.580
Peng.

22:22.370 --> 22:23.150
Peng.

22:23.180 --> 22:23.860
By the way,

22:24.650 --> 22:26.040
I forgot to answer your question.

22:28.080 --> 22:29.580
I studied medicine because

22:29.610 --> 22:31.400
someone used to get hurt a lot.

22:31.560 --> 22:33.320
I thought when I became a doctor,

22:34.050 --> 22:35.360
I could take better care of her.

22:46.180 --> 22:47.380
Auntie.

22:49.350 --> 22:50.140
Auntie.

22:53.230 --> 22:54.120
What's wrong?

22:55.190 --> 22:56.050
Auntie.

22:59.050 --> 23:00.100
Wen Peng.

23:00.480 --> 23:01.870
What are you trying to say now?

23:10.170 --> 23:11.230
I know you've suffered a lot

23:11.270 --> 23:12.630
all these years,

23:13.150 --> 23:15.250
but she's your biological mother.

23:16.100 --> 23:17.610
Be nice to her.

23:18.620 --> 23:19.410
What are you doing?

23:20.000 --> 23:20.900
Trying to lecture me?

23:22.050 --> 23:22.890
I'm not.

23:24.150 --> 23:24.670
It's just advice.

23:25.990 --> 23:26.750
I'm afraid you'll regret it.

23:28.670 --> 23:29.570
Regret?

23:30.510 --> 23:31.750
Why are you and she appearing

23:31.770 --> 23:33.060
in front of me at the same time?

23:35.900 --> 23:37.110
Do you want to embarrass me

23:37.150 --> 23:38.030
in front of Lu Yan?

23:40.350 --> 23:41.760
You overthink.

23:41.870 --> 23:43.210
Then, why did you show up?

23:44.460 --> 23:45.970
She misses you.

23:46.180 --> 23:47.490
I'm afraid she might be

23:47.720 --> 23:48.870
in danger to be here.

23:50.060 --> 23:50.700
Danger?

23:52.510 --> 23:53.730
Am I that danger?

23:54.250 --> 23:55.360
I didn't say it was you.

24:01.280 --> 24:02.150
Arrest me.

24:06.040 --> 24:06.670
Arrest…

24:08.150 --> 24:09.220
Or not.

24:18.920 --> 24:19.970
Jiang Chengyi.

24:20.900 --> 24:22.170
Auntie passed out.

24:29.080 --> 24:30.620
According to the test data,

24:30.650 --> 24:31.720
there's nothing serious.

24:32.040 --> 24:33.270
It's just her blood pressure is a little high.

24:34.150 --> 24:34.950
Sir,

24:35.310 --> 24:36.470
how was her blood pressure

24:36.510 --> 24:37.210
before?

24:37.610 --> 24:39.430
People at this age all have slightly high blood pressure. She's no exception.

24:39.550 --> 24:40.920
But it has been quite stable.

24:41.110 --> 24:42.190
Well then, it was because

24:42.350 --> 24:43.390
she became too emotional.

24:43.610 --> 24:44.590
It's fine. Just be careful.

24:45.450 --> 24:45.980
Okay.

24:47.070 --> 24:47.730
Ma'am.

24:49.050 --> 24:49.960
Don't move.

24:49.990 --> 24:51.020
You have an IV needle in your hand.

24:51.970 --> 24:53.650
How do you feel now?

24:53.860 --> 24:54.940
Does your head still hurt?

24:57.400 --> 24:58.240
No.

24:58.590 --> 24:59.300
Okay.

24:59.360 --> 25:01.050
Tell us if you need anything.

25:02.830 --> 25:03.790
Ma'am is awake.

25:03.870 --> 25:04.610
I think

25:04.630 --> 25:06.270
there's no problem now.

25:06.560 --> 25:08.110
Keep an eye on her tonight.

25:08.270 --> 25:09.590
If she has a headache

25:09.630 --> 25:10.550
or feels sick,

25:10.630 --> 25:11.720
let us know immediately.

25:11.920 --> 25:12.440
Okay.

25:12.710 --> 25:13.820
I'll leave if there's nothing else.

25:14.830 --> 25:15.500
Lu,

25:15.600 --> 25:16.640
call me if you need anything.

25:16.660 --> 25:17.290
I'm leaving.

25:17.310 --> 25:18.160
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

25:18.240 --> 25:18.830
It's nothing.

25:24.850 --> 25:26.540
Why am I in the hospital?

25:27.340 --> 25:28.060
Auntie.

25:28.110 --> 25:29.170
You fainted.

25:31.310 --> 25:31.990
Chengyi.

25:33.680 --> 25:34.640
Where is Wen Peng?

25:36.150 --> 25:37.930
Don't think about these things for now.

25:38.300 --> 25:39.510
Take good care of yourself first.

25:40.400 --> 25:41.190
Don't get worked up again.

25:41.890 --> 25:42.640
Did you...

25:43.390 --> 25:44.770
Did you two fight?

25:46.780 --> 25:47.990
Don't worry about that.

25:48.490 --> 25:49.460
Take care of yourself.

25:57.250 --> 25:58.170
Dad.

25:59.430 --> 26:00.200
You stay here.

26:00.230 --> 26:02.420
I'll go down and buy some drinks.

26:02.510 --> 26:03.270
Okay, go ahead.

26:03.310 --> 26:04.030
I'll go with you.

26:14.270 --> 26:15.470
Have something warm to drink.

26:27.350 --> 26:28.150
Jiang Chengyi,

26:30.100 --> 26:31.360
if...

26:33.480 --> 26:34.860
I mean if,

26:36.920 --> 26:38.870
if Wen Peng is behind all this,

26:41.260 --> 26:42.440
what will you do?

26:44.070 --> 26:45.700
Do what I should do.

26:46.930 --> 26:48.090
I can't compromise on this.

26:50.570 --> 26:52.640
But Auntie will be very sad

26:54.390 --> 26:55.960
with her health condition like that.

27:00.420 --> 27:02.360
I hope she can understand me.

27:03.510 --> 27:04.760
There's no other way.

27:18.900 --> 27:19.480
Come on.

27:19.860 --> 27:20.690
Stop crying.

27:29.410 --> 27:30.730
Why are you laughing?

27:30.850 --> 27:31.960
It just occurred to me

27:31.990 --> 27:33.080
that twenty years ago,

27:33.550 --> 27:35.620
there was a pretty girl

27:36.030 --> 27:37.700
at Chengyi's after-school care.

27:38.030 --> 27:39.890
She cried every day.

27:40.450 --> 27:42.180
I was wondering

27:42.200 --> 27:43.750
what exactly happened to her.

27:43.830 --> 27:45.550
Why did she cry every day?

27:45.870 --> 27:47.480
Why didn't she come to me,

27:47.510 --> 27:48.470
a handsome

27:48.490 --> 27:50.350
and righteous police officer,

27:50.390 --> 27:51.530
and ask me to save her?

27:52.930 --> 27:53.970
Narcissistic.

27:55.300 --> 27:56.320
Even at such a young age,

27:56.340 --> 27:57.110
Chengyi figured it out.

27:57.570 --> 27:58.790
I went to pick him up that day.

27:59.060 --> 28:00.470
He dragged you to me

28:00.510 --> 28:01.630
and asked you to report to the police.

28:01.700 --> 28:02.580
You remember it, right?

28:02.860 --> 28:04.000
At that time,

28:05.840 --> 28:07.760
Wen Peng's father didn't allow me to see him.

28:10.230 --> 28:12.000
What's the use of reporting to the police?

28:13.690 --> 28:14.830
Enough.

28:14.850 --> 28:16.200
Stop thinking about it.

28:17.100 --> 28:18.670
No need to feel guilty.

28:19.230 --> 28:21.310
You never abandoned him.

28:28.450 --> 28:29.550
Didn't you meet him

28:29.550 --> 28:30.630
today?

28:31.290 --> 28:32.730
The hardest part is getting started.

28:33.000 --> 28:34.190
I told you,

28:34.220 --> 28:35.070
as long as we

28:35.110 --> 28:37.000
treat him sincerely,

28:37.350 --> 28:38.190
sooner or later,

28:38.230 --> 28:39.270
he will accept you.

28:40.470 --> 28:41.420
Don't cry anymore.

28:41.590 --> 28:42.210
Look.

28:42.250 --> 28:43.480
You're crying again.

28:46.110 --> 28:47.150
Are you hungry?

28:47.320 --> 28:47.930
Yes.

28:48.550 --> 28:49.210
Shall I make some porridge?

28:50.920 --> 28:51.660
You want porridge, right?

28:51.680 --> 28:52.250
Okay.

28:52.710 --> 28:53.750
You're not seriously ill.

28:53.780 --> 28:54.390
Why do you want porridge?

28:54.440 --> 28:54.670
Come on.

28:54.690 --> 28:55.590
Let's go out and have a meal

28:55.590 --> 28:56.300
in a restaurant.

28:56.390 --> 28:57.740
Go away.

30:04.550 --> 30:05.110
Senior.

30:05.710 --> 30:06.790
What are you doing?

30:08.000 --> 30:08.670
I'm reading.

30:09.560 --> 30:10.160
What about you?

30:10.770 --> 30:11.760
I'm running.

30:11.790 --> 30:13.230
The physical test is coming.

30:13.250 --> 30:14.200
I'm training for it.

30:17.390 --> 30:18.600
I'm off to run, then.

30:19.450 --> 30:20.050
Okay, go for it!

30:49.430 --> 30:50.640
[Wang Qianqian Dead]

30:50.640 --> 30:52.580
[Yu Bofeng—News about foster mother Wang Dan; Targeting the police officer Jiang Chengyi]

30:52.650 --> 30:57.760
[Jiang Chengyi—Has the same mother He Yan; Rival in love]

30:52.950 --> 30:54.460
If that's the case,

30:54.630 --> 30:55.880
Wen Peng does

30:55.910 --> 30:57.190
have enough motive.

30:58.090 --> 30:59.470
But the problem is

31:00.070 --> 31:01.330
we're just suspecting that,

31:01.470 --> 31:02.150
but we don't have

31:02.190 --> 31:03.070
solid evidence yet.

31:02.640 --> 31:07.320
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

31:04.070 --> 31:05.550
He is meticulous,

31:06.350 --> 31:07.310
extreme,

31:07.440 --> 31:09.010
and good at manipulating people's hearts.

31:09.040 --> 31:09.900
Besides,

31:09.990 --> 31:12.340
he has some clout in society

31:13.160 --> 31:14.780
We've been investigating for so long,

31:14.800 --> 31:16.480
yet he didn't slip up at all.

31:17.030 --> 31:18.430
It couldn't be done by one person.

31:19.660 --> 31:20.790
I think there must be someone else

31:20.830 --> 31:22.140
other than Li Ruonan.

31:22.190 --> 31:23.290
Whether the ones

31:23.310 --> 31:24.760
who spread the rumor online,

31:24.790 --> 31:25.810
or

31:26.070 --> 31:27.370
the truck driver,

31:26.340 --> 31:28.900
[Driver]

31:28.800 --> 31:30.150
He can't find them himself.

31:31.090 --> 31:32.310
He must have someone

31:32.330 --> 31:33.280
to do these things for him.

31:33.310 --> 31:35.130
And it must be someone around him.

31:35.660 --> 31:36.280
It's easy to control.

31:38.940 --> 31:39.470
Yiming.

31:40.400 --> 31:41.900
Take a look at

31:41.920 --> 31:44.740
those close to Wen Peng,

31:44.760 --> 31:46.550
whether subordinates

31:46.760 --> 31:48.360
or friends.

31:49.280 --> 31:50.550
Go through everyone around him

31:50.870 --> 31:52.060
and see if there's

31:52.110 --> 31:53.020
useful evidence.

31:53.240 --> 31:53.780
Understood.

31:54.150 --> 31:54.770
Senior.

31:55.520 --> 31:57.030
I want to go to his crew.

31:57.280 --> 31:58.200
For what?

31:58.600 --> 31:59.670
Recently,

32:00.400 --> 32:01.350
I've learned some

32:01.350 --> 32:02.630
about the makeup of the crew.

32:03.150 --> 32:04.080
The regular staff

32:04.100 --> 32:05.720
comes from

32:05.750 --> 32:06.750
all over.

32:06.900 --> 32:07.910
They are not from the same place.

32:08.030 --> 32:09.540
But once a project starts,

32:09.920 --> 32:11.230
they will gather together

32:11.310 --> 32:12.070
from different places

32:12.070 --> 32:13.080
to live together for a period of time.

32:13.160 --> 32:13.920
So, did Li Ruonan

32:13.950 --> 32:15.270
have friends

32:15.340 --> 32:16.550
or acquaintances?

32:16.570 --> 32:17.470
I'd like to see if there are any clues.

32:17.920 --> 32:19.670
I don't think it's very likely.

32:20.170 --> 32:28.290
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

32:20.230 --> 32:21.920
No news from Professor Yu yet?

32:24.620 --> 32:25.350
Alright.

32:26.030 --> 32:27.170
Get to work.

32:34.420 --> 32:41.780
[Public Security]

32:36.520 --> 32:37.360
Yu Bofeng.

32:37.730 --> 32:39.180
Check your personal belongings.

32:39.210 --> 32:40.230
Sign here.

32:44.630 --> 32:48.420
[Public Security]

32:46.660 --> 32:47.670
Here is a letter

32:47.670 --> 32:48.510
from Ms. Yu.

32:52.040 --> 32:56.450
[To Yu Bofeng]

33:04.990 --> 33:14.360
[Public Security]

33:17.840 --> 33:19.310
Sorry, Peng.

33:19.750 --> 33:20.870
Don't say sorry.

33:21.480 --> 33:22.260
You have me.

33:24.390 --> 33:24.910
Peng.

33:27.690 --> 33:29.020
I only have you now.

33:30.860 --> 33:31.350
All right.

33:31.370 --> 33:32.200
Go home.

33:39.060 --> 33:40.050
During this period,

33:40.080 --> 33:41.670
take a good rest

33:41.870 --> 33:43.270
and adjust yourself.

33:44.250 --> 33:45.520
I don't need to rest.

33:46.940 --> 33:48.770
I've had enough rest inside.

33:48.800 --> 33:49.820
Now I'm out,

33:49.870 --> 33:51.230
I won't do anything else anymore.

33:52.680 --> 33:53.840
I just want both of them

33:53.870 --> 33:55.270
to pay the price.

33:58.630 --> 33:59.900
Actually, when you were in there,

33:59.940 --> 34:01.690
it was inconvenient for me to tell you some things.

34:02.990 --> 34:04.070
But

34:04.500 --> 34:05.930
they've started to hate me.

34:09.239 --> 34:10.350
But it's okay.

34:10.530 --> 34:12.120
They're the police after all.

34:13.310 --> 34:14.170
Bear with it.

34:14.190 --> 34:15.239
Why should I?

34:15.909 --> 34:17.199
Just because they are the police,

34:17.230 --> 34:17.830
I have to endure it?

34:18.350 --> 34:20.330
So what if they are the police?

34:21.440 --> 34:22.730
Now,

34:22.760 --> 34:23.909
I have nothing!

34:26.429 --> 34:28.170
I want revenge even if it costs my life!

34:34.350 --> 34:36.000
Peng, help me.

34:42.880 --> 34:43.510
Hello.

34:43.889 --> 34:44.639
Mr. Wen.

34:44.730 --> 34:45.989
Some police officers came here.

34:46.090 --> 34:48.000
They said they wanted to ask

34:48.070 --> 34:49.389
some questions to the crew members..

34:49.570 --> 34:50.300
Okay, I got it.

34:50.330 --> 34:51.469
I'll be right there.

34:51.750 --> 34:52.960
What is your main job

34:52.989 --> 34:54.260
in this crew?

34:54.530 --> 34:55.480
On-site coordination.

34:57.510 --> 34:58.990
Do you know everyone?

34:59.020 --> 34:59.640
Mr. Wen.

34:59.670 --> 35:00.270
Basically.

35:00.270 --> 35:00.630
This way.

35:00.770 --> 35:01.840
We're an old team.

35:01.880 --> 35:03.070
Are you familiar with your boss?

35:03.110 --> 35:03.950
How many times have you worked together?

35:04.990 --> 35:06.300
It's okay. Go back to work.

35:06.990 --> 35:07.590
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

35:07.630 --> 35:08.290
Thank you.

35:08.590 --> 35:09.450
Let me introduce you.

35:09.500 --> 35:10.500
This is Mr. Wen.

35:10.550 --> 35:11.150
I know him.

35:11.410 --> 35:12.140
Mr. Wen.

35:12.600 --> 35:13.560
I'm Qin Yue

35:13.630 --> 35:14.800
from the Criminal Investigation Unit of Anshan District.

35:14.860 --> 35:15.730
Hello, Mr. Wen.

35:17.070 --> 35:17.880
Officer Qin, what are you

35:17.910 --> 35:18.990
investigating today?

35:19.020 --> 35:19.860
No, it's not an investigation.

35:20.350 --> 35:21.100
It's just

35:21.120 --> 35:22.740
to get some general information.

35:24.140 --> 35:25.630
What, Mr. Wen,

35:25.990 --> 35:27.090
you don't welcome us?

35:27.820 --> 35:28.250
How come?

35:29.330 --> 35:30.400
As you can see,

35:30.430 --> 35:31.890
our crew is busy.

35:31.990 --> 35:32.590
So,

35:33.450 --> 35:34.230
please understand.

35:34.270 --> 35:35.030
Don't worry, Mr. Wen.

35:35.030 --> 35:35.890
We understand.

35:35.920 --> 35:37.080
We know what to do.

35:37.180 --> 35:38.380
We work normally,

35:38.410 --> 35:39.570
and you work normally, as well.

35:39.600 --> 35:40.800
We won't affect each other.

35:41.100 --> 35:41.510
Okay.

35:41.530 --> 35:42.550
I understand what you mean.

35:42.920 --> 35:44.040
We work normally.

35:44.070 --> 35:45.190
You investigate normally.

35:45.360 --> 35:46.760
It's getting some general information.

35:52.420 --> 35:53.340
Everyone, listen up.

35:54.980 --> 35:55.670
Let's call it a day.

35:56.180 --> 35:57.110
What do you mean?

35:57.110 --> 35:57.550
Nothing.

35:58.240 --> 35:59.420
Get ready to wrap up.

35:59.710 --> 36:01.350
Okay.

36:01.380 --> 36:02.010
You're wrapping up?

36:04.400 --> 36:05.730
Let's call it a day, too.

36:07.020 --> 36:08.640
But if

36:08.670 --> 36:09.310
our work requires it,

36:09.310 --> 36:10.590
we may come back tomorrow and the day after it.

36:10.620 --> 36:12.150
I hope you'll welcome us, Mr. Wen.

36:12.170 --> 36:13.140
No problem.

36:13.170 --> 36:13.860
Thank you, Mr. Wen.

36:13.890 --> 36:14.520
Thank you.

36:17.390 --> 36:18.190
Wait.

36:21.560 --> 36:23.100
Tell Captain Jiang

36:23.410 --> 36:24.720
if he doesn't have any clues,

36:24.740 --> 36:25.470
he can come to me.

36:25.490 --> 36:26.290
I can help him.

36:29.070 --> 36:30.400
Then, I can answer you

36:30.430 --> 36:32.630
for Captain Jiang now.

36:33.780 --> 36:34.490
No need.

36:36.120 --> 36:37.050
I'm leaving. Bye.

36:37.890 --> 36:38.490
Thank you.

36:52.050 --> 36:52.690
Peng.

36:58.990 --> 36:59.550
Peng.

37:00.170 --> 37:01.650
Why did the police go to the set?

37:01.790 --> 37:04.090
Jiang Chengyi sent someone to the set.

37:04.470 --> 37:05.430
To investigate?

37:06.160 --> 37:07.380
What can they investigate?

37:07.640 --> 37:08.820
I don't know.

37:10.380 --> 37:12.300
They said they were just investigating,

37:12.750 --> 37:14.290
so I asked the crew to call it a day.

37:16.030 --> 37:17.250
But they said

37:17.540 --> 37:18.750
they would come back again

37:20.840 --> 37:22.030
in the upcoming period.

37:24.150 --> 37:25.310
Jiang Chengyi!

37:25.390 --> 37:27.070
Jiang Chengyi is so annoying.

37:30.510 --> 37:31.430
I think

37:31.570 --> 37:33.070
during the time ahead,

37:33.190 --> 37:34.510
the company will face a lot of trouble.

37:35.040 --> 37:36.160
You did nothing wrong.

37:36.190 --> 37:37.550
Why are they targeting you?

37:40.590 --> 37:41.750
I did nothing wrong.

37:43.500 --> 37:44.850
But have you ever thought that

37:45.470 --> 37:46.630
you worked for my company?

37:47.080 --> 37:47.830
Everything they do now

37:47.870 --> 37:48.550
is

37:48.590 --> 37:49.710
for revenge.

37:56.120 --> 37:57.290
I'm sorry, Peng.

38:00.190 --> 38:01.150
It's all my fault.

38:02.000 --> 38:02.720
I've dragged you into this.

38:08.110 --> 38:08.790
Alright.

38:09.310 --> 38:09.960
Let's not talk about this.

38:11.700 --> 38:12.360
Bofeng,

38:13.010 --> 38:15.070
many things will happen in the future.

38:15.570 --> 38:17.040
But you must remember:

38:17.850 --> 38:18.860
Let bygones

38:18.880 --> 38:19.980
be bygones.

38:20.190 --> 38:21.070
I hope you can

38:21.110 --> 38:23.220
discard the unpleasant thoughts.

38:23.470 --> 38:25.060
Once all of this is over,

38:25.110 --> 38:26.300
I'll find a chance

38:27.250 --> 38:27.840
to give you a push.

38:28.710 --> 38:31.390
Let's start over.

38:33.330 --> 38:33.830
But...

38:34.370 --> 38:36.110
I can't just swallow this

38:36.150 --> 38:37.390
no matter what.

38:37.820 --> 38:38.830
Why can't you understand

38:38.850 --> 38:39.750
what I'm talking about?

38:41.230 --> 38:42.110
Don't you know

38:42.130 --> 38:42.900
their approaches?

38:43.500 --> 38:45.330
We are very passive now.

38:45.350 --> 38:46.900
I don't want you to get involved again.

38:51.670 --> 38:52.830
I'm not afraid of

38:52.850 --> 38:53.790
anything now.

38:53.810 --> 38:55.280
I don't care anymore!

38:55.310 --> 38:56.960
Calm down.

38:57.170 --> 38:57.950
Okay?

39:00.620 --> 39:01.950
I understand how you feel.

39:01.980 --> 39:03.040
But can you

39:03.110 --> 39:04.590
stop stressing over things about

39:04.610 --> 39:05.770
Jiang Chengyi and Yu Zheng?

39:05.800 --> 39:06.120
Okay?

39:06.140 --> 39:06.900
But this kind of thing

39:06.930 --> 39:08.310
has already implicated you…

39:13.380 --> 39:14.480
Calm down.

39:15.130 --> 39:16.170
Calm down.

39:17.220 --> 39:17.960
Reason.

39:18.500 --> 39:19.760
Be rational.

39:21.790 --> 39:23.230
You just want to vent your anger, don't you?

39:23.920 --> 39:24.670
Fine.

39:25.980 --> 39:27.750
I'll find someone to teach them a lesson.

39:29.080 --> 39:30.460
We don't even need to get involved.

39:33.220 --> 39:33.860
Okay?

39:49.320 --> 39:49.930
Professor Yu,

39:50.070 --> 39:51.350
I contacted the Health Commission in Chengzhou

39:51.370 --> 39:52.070
and found that Yan Mei

39:52.110 --> 39:53.230
was once treated in Chengzhou

39:53.250 --> 39:53.720
Second People's Hospital.

39:57.250 --> 39:58.070
Okay.

39:58.620 --> 39:59.840
Let's go to

39:59.870 --> 40:00.590
the Second People's Hospital tomorrow.

40:00.790 --> 40:01.440
Okay.

40:01.630 --> 40:02.420
Rest early.

40:20.380 --> 40:23.840
[Yu Bofeng Regains His Freedom: From A Big Star to A Life With a Criminal Record]

40:43.430 --> 40:46.410
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

40:48.630 --> 40:49.280
Hello.

40:49.300 --> 40:50.140
Are you busy?

40:50.160 --> 40:50.910
Dr. Han.

40:50.940 --> 40:52.060
Dr. Han.

40:53.630 --> 40:54.350
Lu.

40:56.250 --> 40:57.210
Why are you sleepy again?

40:57.240 --> 40:58.280
You didn't sleep well last night?

40:58.300 --> 40:59.520
No.

40:59.700 --> 41:01.380
Jiang Chengyi’s mother is in hospital.

41:01.470 --> 41:02.390
Jiang Chengyi and I

41:02.410 --> 41:03.750
stayed overnight with her last night.

41:03.990 --> 41:04.790
She's hospitalized?

41:04.820 --> 41:05.870
Is it that serious?

41:06.040 --> 41:06.640
No.

41:06.820 --> 41:07.840
She's fine now.

41:09.010 --> 41:10.540
What's up?

41:11.870 --> 41:13.240
Your mother's

41:13.340 --> 41:14.520
test result is out.

41:14.750 --> 41:15.600
Didn't she

41:15.630 --> 41:17.220
have a polyp in her stomach?

41:17.720 --> 41:18.660
When we checked it before,

41:18.710 --> 41:19.950
it was very small. There was no need to deal with it.

41:20.150 --> 41:21.430
But this time we found

41:21.760 --> 41:23.000
it has grown bigger.

41:23.920 --> 41:25.600
It's 0.6.

41:25.060 --> 41:27.430
[Painless Gastroscopy Report]

41:25.840 --> 41:27.000
We have to cut it right away.

41:27.020 --> 41:27.720
Yes.

41:27.920 --> 41:29.330
That's what I mean.

41:29.480 --> 41:30.400
If it gets bigger,

41:30.430 --> 41:31.360
we need to perform an open surgery.

41:32.080 --> 41:33.180
Thank you, Dr. Han.

41:33.270 --> 41:34.150
Thanks to you.

41:34.190 --> 41:36.310
What should I do without you?

41:37.900 --> 41:39.610
You've become so sweet.

41:41.410 --> 41:42.620
Lu, have you noticed that

41:42.920 --> 41:45.610
since you started dating,

41:46.500 --> 41:48.020
your temper has improved,

41:48.230 --> 41:50.070
and you've stopped bugging me to review your thesis.

41:51.090 --> 41:51.730
Thesis?

41:51.760 --> 41:53.650
It's about to finish!

41:53.770 --> 41:54.290
I...

41:54.310 --> 41:54.720
Don't.

41:54.740 --> 41:55.240
Don't.

41:55.490 --> 41:56.380
Take your time.

41:56.480 --> 41:57.860
Read it several more times.

41:57.890 --> 41:58.660
Make it perfect.

42:00.210 --> 42:00.910
Okay.

42:01.440 --> 42:02.980
I'll tell my mom about this first.

42:03.010 --> 42:03.990
Okay, go ahead.

42:04.030 --> 42:04.880
Take your time.

42:04.910 --> 42:05.580
Thank you.

42:05.600 --> 42:06.350
No rush.

42:06.370 --> 42:06.910
Okay.

42:10.140 --> 42:11.030
Mom.

42:12.240 --> 42:13.830
Where are you? It's so noisy at your end.

42:13.850 --> 42:15.120
I'm in Harbin.

42:15.160 --> 42:16.390
I'm going skiing.

42:16.420 --> 42:16.870
What's wrong?

42:16.890 --> 42:17.600
Skiing?

42:17.630 --> 42:18.660
Your medical report

42:18.680 --> 42:19.630
is out.

42:19.750 --> 42:21.410
You need to come back for an operation.

42:21.440 --> 42:22.620
The polyps are growing.

42:23.590 --> 42:25.200
Go back again?

42:25.290 --> 42:26.570
I'll just find a hospital here

42:26.600 --> 42:28.120
to do it.

42:28.640 --> 42:29.920
I don't believe you will do it.

42:29.950 --> 42:30.920
Come back soon.

42:31.380 --> 42:32.820
I just came back and now I need to go back again.

42:32.910 --> 42:34.390
Do you think the flight ticket is free?

42:34.670 --> 42:35.630
I'll buy it for you.

42:35.650 --> 42:36.220
Okay?

42:36.800 --> 42:38.070
It's a deal, then.

42:39.710 --> 42:40.460
Lu Yan.

42:43.030 --> 42:43.990
Why are you here?

42:44.220 --> 42:44.960
Have you eaten?

42:45.200 --> 42:45.770
No.

42:45.850 --> 42:46.920
I brought you lunch.

42:48.060 --> 42:48.980
Thank you.

42:49.920 --> 42:50.710
How is my mom?

42:50.890 --> 42:52.230
She's fine.

42:52.250 --> 42:53.240
She can be discharged

42:53.260 --> 42:54.180
after being monitored for one more afternoon.

42:53.730 --> 42:55.230
♫As the city flickers♫

42:54.260 --> 42:55.470
I'll go through the procedures later.

42:56.430 --> 42:59.330
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

42:57.310 --> 42:59.170
Will you have dinner with me?

42:59.940 --> 43:01.320
I have an operation later.

43:00.490 --> 43:01.950
♫And you, who love to smile♫

43:01.350 --> 43:02.150
I might get off work late.

43:02.540 --> 43:03.980
It's okay. I'll pick you up after work.

43:02.800 --> 43:05.580
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

43:05.250 --> 43:05.830
Okay.

43:06.190 --> 43:07.070
Come with me.

43:06.290 --> 43:08.630
♫The humor of time♫

43:07.230 --> 43:07.630
Okay.

43:21.390 --> 43:21.970
Mom.

43:22.810 --> 43:24.040
Don't overthink.

43:24.220 --> 43:25.060
Your health is more important.

43:26.560 --> 43:27.880
I let Peng down.

43:32.500 --> 43:33.670
To be honest,

43:35.890 --> 43:37.430
all these years, I haven't spent one day

43:37.500 --> 43:38.360
without thinking about him.

43:40.540 --> 43:42.440
Watching you grow up every day,

43:43.750 --> 43:44.930
I thought

43:46.620 --> 43:47.640
if Peng

43:49.320 --> 43:50.360
was as tall as

43:50.380 --> 43:51.670
Chengyi

43:53.110 --> 43:56.720
and as sensible as him?

44:02.060 --> 44:03.540
If I knew this would happen,

44:04.330 --> 44:05.600
no matter how hard it was,

44:06.520 --> 44:07.820
I should have brought him along.

44:10.020 --> 44:11.790
All these years have passed.

44:12.570 --> 44:14.440
And he's an adult.

44:15.870 --> 44:17.350
Some things just can't be forced,

44:18.190 --> 44:19.150
so don't try to push it.

44:27.070 --> 44:27.900
Chengyi,

44:33.990 --> 44:35.650
thank you for understanding me.

44:39.600 --> 44:40.800
I may not be able to

44:42.340 --> 44:43.500
fully empathize

44:43.550 --> 44:44.510
with these things.

44:46.200 --> 44:47.570
But I know

44:47.670 --> 44:49.580
you can't give up this kind of relationship.

44:52.340 --> 44:53.200
I understand.

44:53.490 --> 44:54.580
What's important is

44:55.050 --> 44:56.270
that you shouldn't overthink.

44:57.010 --> 44:58.210
Your health is the most important.

44:58.440 --> 44:59.120
Right?

45:16.960 --> 45:20.550
[Doctor's Office, Chengzhou Second People's Hospital]

45:17.710 --> 45:18.860
Yan Mei?

45:20.710 --> 45:21.750
Yes, we found that

45:21.790 --> 45:22.670
she was treated by you

45:22.690 --> 45:23.730
for a while.

45:23.840 --> 45:25.200
So, we came here to find out more about it.

45:30.340 --> 45:31.290
I remember.

45:31.540 --> 45:32.730
She's my patient.

45:33.310 --> 45:34.310
Can you tell us

45:34.350 --> 45:35.190
what happened at that time?

45:37.260 --> 45:39.040
When Yan Mei was hospitalized,

45:39.360 --> 45:41.010
she was seriously ill.

45:41.280 --> 45:42.510
She needs dialysis every week.

45:43.410 --> 45:44.570
Do you remember

45:44.630 --> 45:45.510
who sent her

45:45.530 --> 45:46.650
to the hospital back then?

45:48.640 --> 45:49.370
No.

45:49.400 --> 45:50.460
She came alone.

45:51.140 --> 45:52.150
Every time she needed to be hospitalized,

45:52.230 --> 45:53.550
she came alone.

45:53.750 --> 45:54.520
So,

45:54.550 --> 45:55.310
I remembered her

45:55.330 --> 45:56.270
pretty clearly.

45:58.350 --> 46:00.110
But I remember she once said

46:00.190 --> 46:01.200
she had a daughter

46:01.310 --> 46:02.150
working in another city.

46:04.030 --> 46:04.710
Then what happened?

46:06.830 --> 46:08.960
She was here for treatment

46:09.190 --> 46:10.680
for half a year,

46:10.790 --> 46:12.640
but her condition had always been rather serious.

46:13.230 --> 46:14.390
I remember in the end,

46:14.430 --> 46:15.390
we also performed a resuscitation

46:15.430 --> 46:16.760
on Yan Mei.

46:16.870 --> 46:18.610
Although she was saved,

46:18.740 --> 46:19.650
but

46:19.680 --> 46:20.470
she had to

46:20.470 --> 46:21.270
undergo a kidney transplant.

46:23.850 --> 46:25.780
In Yan Mei's case,

46:25.910 --> 46:26.980
there's no other way

46:27.000 --> 46:28.560
but to have a kidney transplant.

46:28.710 --> 46:29.600
But we understand her

46:29.620 --> 46:30.760
when she asked to be discharged.

46:30.810 --> 46:31.790
As far as big surgeries

46:31.790 --> 46:32.710
like kidney transplants are concerned,

46:33.030 --> 46:33.870
the cost

46:34.010 --> 46:35.000
is one issue,

46:35.330 --> 46:36.240
and finding a donor

46:36.260 --> 46:37.520
is another big problem.

46:37.800 --> 46:39.820
She had always been alone.

46:39.930 --> 46:40.820
Did anyone take care of her

46:40.870 --> 46:41.750
when she was hospitalized?

46:42.090 --> 46:42.900
Yes.

46:43.180 --> 46:44.230
She had a caretaker

46:44.310 --> 46:44.980
taking care of her.

46:45.270 --> 46:46.830
The caregiver was helping her

46:46.850 --> 46:47.900
with things like

46:47.920 --> 46:49.820
paying bills, nursing, and contacting her family.

46:50.360 --> 46:51.760
Is the caretaker still here?

46:51.780 --> 46:53.110
I don't know.

46:53.380 --> 46:54.100
However,

46:54.120 --> 46:54.790
you can go to

46:54.830 --> 46:55.630
the Health Department of our hospital

46:55.670 --> 46:56.190
to find out.

46:56.470 --> 46:57.150
They have the information

46:57.170 --> 46:58.520
of all the caretakers.

47:00.950 --> 47:01.710
So,

47:01.710 --> 47:02.860
Ma Cheng is the caretaker

47:02.950 --> 47:03.630
who has been taking care of

47:03.630 --> 47:04.710
Li Ruonan's mother.

47:04.870 --> 47:05.970
After Yan Mei was discharged,

47:06.150 --> 47:06.990
he resigned.

47:08.250 --> 47:09.700
We need to find him as soon as possible.

47:10.320 --> 47:11.230
Contact

47:11.230 --> 47:12.340
the local police station

47:12.370 --> 47:13.630
and find Ma Cheng's contact information

47:13.660 --> 47:14.580
and his home address.

47:15.070 --> 47:15.470
Okay.

47:19.790 --> 47:21.230
End-stage uremia?

47:22.340 --> 47:23.210
Yes.

47:23.270 --> 47:24.110
The doctor said

47:24.150 --> 47:25.510
when she left the hospital,

47:25.530 --> 47:26.130
her physical condition

47:26.160 --> 47:27.350
was very serious.

47:27.690 --> 47:28.990
I guess there were only two reasons

47:29.030 --> 47:30.150
why she left the hospital.

47:30.740 --> 47:32.160
Either she went to a better hospital

47:32.190 --> 47:33.480
for better treatment,

47:33.640 --> 47:34.570
or…

47:34.690 --> 47:38.600
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

47:34.980 --> 47:36.750
She just gave up treatment.

47:37.960 --> 47:38.680
Yes.

47:38.900 --> 47:40.520
We have found

47:40.550 --> 47:41.640
Ma Cheng's address.

47:41.850 --> 47:42.830
We're on our way there.

47:42.850 --> 47:43.250
Okay.

47:43.930 --> 47:45.260
Be careful.

47:45.520 --> 47:46.390
Don't worry.

47:46.410 --> 47:47.030
If anything happens,

47:47.070 --> 47:48.230
I'll tell you anytime.

48:00.940 --> 48:01.840
Bofeng.

48:02.750 --> 48:03.270
Why haven't you

48:03.310 --> 48:04.310
sent me any messages all day?

48:05.080 --> 48:06.040
Listen to me.

48:06.200 --> 48:07.060
Don't be impulsive.

48:07.100 --> 48:07.800
Got it?

48:08.150 --> 48:09.080
Don't make me worry.

48:14.790 --> 48:15.630
Do you think I can't find you

48:15.670 --> 48:16.790
if you hide here?

48:17.000 --> 48:18.360
Brat.

48:21.170 --> 48:21.950
Tell me.

48:21.980 --> 48:23.440
Why are you avoiding me?

48:23.870 --> 48:25.040
I'm asking you.

48:25.060 --> 48:26.380
Let's talk inside.

48:26.700 --> 48:28.080
I want to talk here.

48:35.910 --> 48:36.830
Fine.

48:38.200 --> 48:39.780
I know you're rich,

48:40.860 --> 48:42.410
but I didn't know you were this rich

48:43.860 --> 48:45.560
or lived in such a big house.

48:47.190 --> 48:48.510
You're living in such a big house,

48:48.540 --> 48:50.460
yet you didn't bring your father here.

48:50.720 --> 48:52.580
You unfilial son!

48:57.340 --> 48:58.360
What do you want?

48:58.380 --> 48:59.840
What do I want?

49:01.060 --> 49:02.610
I want you!

49:03.160 --> 49:04.210
My son!

49:05.370 --> 49:07.250
I want my sensible

49:07.310 --> 49:08.230
and obedient son,

49:08.680 --> 49:10.660
who behaves well whenever he sees me!

49:12.320 --> 49:13.440
What do I want?

49:17.270 --> 49:18.310
What?

49:19.360 --> 49:20.770
It's such a big house.

49:20.790 --> 49:21.820
Who are you living with?

49:23.330 --> 49:24.340
I live alone.

49:28.120 --> 49:29.820
I knew it.

49:30.340 --> 49:32.400
You may be rich now,

49:34.830 --> 49:35.510
but you…

49:37.150 --> 49:39.430
are just something that no one wants.

49:41.030 --> 49:41.970
How about this?

49:42.540 --> 49:43.710
From now on,

49:43.880 --> 49:45.080
I will live here.

49:45.760 --> 49:47.180
I'm your father, after all.

49:48.050 --> 49:49.390
I don't mind you.

49:50.310 --> 49:51.790
You know.

49:54.630 --> 49:55.720
I told you

49:55.740 --> 49:57.110
we had no connection anymore.

49:57.830 --> 49:59.030
What did you say?

50:00.880 --> 50:01.850
No connection?

50:06.650 --> 50:07.870
Look at me and tell me.

50:08.580 --> 50:09.500
Who am I?

50:10.760 --> 50:11.920
Who am I?

50:12.560 --> 50:13.540
Let me tell you.

50:13.600 --> 50:14.790
I'm your dad.

50:14.870 --> 50:16.030
I'm your father!

50:16.060 --> 50:17.770
Do you know that blood is thicker than water?

50:17.790 --> 50:18.820
If you keep saying it,

50:18.910 --> 50:20.230
I'll sue you!

50:20.800 --> 50:22.400
Remember this, you punk.

50:23.090 --> 50:24.570
In this world,

50:24.690 --> 50:26.230
no one cares about you

50:26.260 --> 50:27.590
or likes you except me.

50:28.020 --> 50:29.330
Since you were little,

50:29.460 --> 50:31.720
no one has ever wanted you.

50:35.350 --> 50:36.340
You're right.

50:37.660 --> 50:38.570
We are the same.

50:39.050 --> 50:39.930
No one wants us.

50:42.120 --> 50:43.510
But I got to where I am today

50:43.550 --> 50:44.590
because of you.

50:45.600 --> 50:46.500
And you are what you are

50:47.720 --> 50:48.980
because of your incompetence.

50:50.660 --> 50:51.900
Say it again.

50:53.750 --> 50:54.890
I said you were incompetent.

50:55.550 --> 50:56.150
That's why you

50:56.180 --> 50:57.380
ended up being betrayed by all.

50:59.500 --> 51:00.920
Brat,

51:00.950 --> 51:02.360
I think your skin is itching.

51:02.430 --> 51:03.230
Right?

51:03.660 --> 51:04.280
I...

51:04.720 --> 51:06.040
I met my mom a few days ago.

51:08.960 --> 51:10.240
Who did you see?

51:10.960 --> 51:12.300
Your mother?

51:12.320 --> 51:13.250
Where did you see her?

51:13.270 --> 51:14.220
What is she doing?

51:14.250 --> 51:15.140
How is she now?

51:15.270 --> 51:16.190
Tell me!

51:16.870 --> 51:18.190
She is in Ninghai right now.

51:18.220 --> 51:19.280
She remarried.

51:19.850 --> 51:21.040
She is very happy.

51:22.360 --> 51:23.550
Her husband is a police officer.

51:23.570 --> 51:24.830
So is her son.

51:26.150 --> 51:27.540
She looks a dozen years

51:27.950 --> 51:29.150
